@startuml
state "Waiting for User" as WaitingUser
state "Checking PIN" as CheckingPIN
state "Invalid PIN" as InvalidPIN
state "Card Held for Security" as CardHeld
state "Options Displayed" as OptionsDisplayed
state "Processing Request" as ProcessingRequest
state "Return Card" as ReturnCard

[*] --> WaitingUser [*]
WaitingUser --> CheckingPIN : user arrives
CheckingPIN --> InvalidPIN : PIN is incorrect
InvalidPIN --> CardHeld : too many attempts
CardHeld --> WaitingUser : card held for security
WaitingUser --> CheckingPIN : retry or cancel
CheckingPIN --> OptionsDisplayed : PIN is correct
OptionsDisplayed --> ProcessingRequest : user selects option
ProcessingRequest --> ReturnCard : request processed

note right of InvalidPIN: "The system shall keep the card for security if it is invalid or the PIN is entered incorrectly too many times."
@enduml
